{"id": 3, "title": "Ticket #3: Customize GitTrac", "description": "<blockquote>\nThis is a ticket to hold everyone's ideas and gripes about Condor's use of gittrac, and what we should change.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2009-Jan-13 12:00:33 by tannenba:</em> <br/>\n\nHow bout getting rid of delete a ticket button and replacing with just a close ticket?\n\n<p>Because ticket ids are re-used after deleting, seems like ticket deletion is a <em>really</em> bad idea.\n\n</p><p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-20 14:26:24 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nThings I've done:\n\n<p></p><ul>\n<li>Replaced the \"closed\" state with \"abandoned\"\n</li><li>Replaced the \"fixed\" state with \"resolved\"\n</li><li>Updated the \"All Tickets\" and \"Tickets for a particular user\" reports to sort by priority, severity, then ticket number, in that order.\n</li></ul>\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-20 15:11:40 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nWhen writing a query to display a ticket number, if the ticket public, just display the number, if the ticket is private, display a 'p' after the number, if the extra3 column is neither private or public, display tn || extra3.\n\n<p>I have updated the queries to perform this.\n\n</p><p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-20 15:55:22 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded a 'stalled' status for when something happens and you can't work on a ticket anymore. Updated the reports to show it properly.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-20 21:29:27 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nFixed all of the reports to honor the status color as a subquery against the enums table. This means in the setup menu, if you change the colors, they will be reflected properly across all the reports automatically. However, the stupid key is still hardcoded, so you're just out of luck on that for now and will have to edit it by hand. If the ticket status or the specific status color isn't in the enums table (which could hold the status colors), then the bgcolor for the row will be white.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-20 21:59:12 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nFixed the coloring of the tickets some more.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-21 11:50:08 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nSorted the tickets in the reports a little better.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-22 00:07:16 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded the \"Developer Plates\" report. It is pretty slick.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-22 00:53:49 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded the ability to pick which status you'd like to see with the developer plate. Of course, it only makes sense if the developer is actually assigned some tickets.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-22 16:07:53 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nWith Alan, prettied up the report a little more. Notably changed the colors and got rid of extraneous information.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-27 10:26:01 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded a drop down for \"All Tickets\" which defaults to ALL and allows you to select what status of tickets you'd like to see.\n\n<p>Also added \"active &amp; stalled\" for the Developer Plate report, since stalled usually means you should be working on it but can't be, so someone should know.\n\n</p><p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Jan-28 18:18:03 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded option dropdowns for Group and Subsystem in the All Tickets report.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Feb-20 13:48:09 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded \"created by\" and \"assigned to\" option boxes for \"All Tickets\" report.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2009-Mar-11 13:20:18 by psilord:</em> <br/>\n\nAdded UNASSIGNED option for 'Assigned To' option box in All Tickets report to select tickets which are not assigned to anyone.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5'); return false;\" title=\"Add CLA field to User table\">#5</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nAdd CLA field to User table</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6'); return false;\" title=\"Remove Delete function for Tickets\">#6</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nRemove Delete function for Tickets</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=28\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('28'); return false;\" title=\"Add e-mail CC column to tickets\">#28</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nAdd e-mail CC column to tickets</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=30\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('30'); return false;\" title=\"Add ability to get email notification on ticket creation\">#30</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nAdd ability to get email notification on ticket creation</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=47\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('47'); return false;\" title=\"Make GitTrac public\">#47</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nMake <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=GitTrac\" title=\"Git Trac\">GitTrac</a></span> public</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=76\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('76'); return false;\" title=\"Color, side-by-side diff\">#76</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nColor, side-by-side diff</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=77\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('77'); return false;\" title=\"Changes to CSS\">#77</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nChanges to CSS</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=118\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('118'); return false;\" title=\"GitTrac: Add ticket to report links\">#118</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\n<span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=GitTrac\" title=\"Git Trac\">GitTrac</a></span>: Add ticket to report links</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=132\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('132'); return false;\" title=\"Fix gittrac style sheet for Internet Explorer\">#132</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nFix gittrac style sheet for Internet Explorer</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=144\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('144'); return false;\" title='Remove \"CondorFW - \" from H1 of Gittrac pages'>#144</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nRemove \"CondorFW - \" from H1 of Gittrac pages</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=147\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('147'); return false;\" title=\"Clarify decription of a ticket priority\">#147</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nClarify decription of a ticket priority</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=148\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('148'); return false;\" title=\"Resolved tickets do not appear w/ strike thru in wiki\">#148</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nResolved tickets do not appear w/ strike thru in wiki</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=150\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('150'); return false;\" title=\"Show ticket when Appending Remarks\">#150</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nShow ticket when Appending Remarks</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=167\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('167'); return false;\" title=\"GitTrac: Diff fails for new files\">#167</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u0